{
  "stem": "23410.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And these-- and everybody got the matzos from the bakery-- you, your own.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You and other people of town baked the matzos.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The influence of the Rebbe was very great-- not only great, but I feel without the Rebbe, my family would have survived.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] It was-- the Rebbe had the absolute influence of life and death of the-- of not real the death, but the life, of every family.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My father that already questioned the idea of the Rebbe-- and he was one of this family-- but basically, couldn't go against it.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He did not allow any of his followers to leave for America or Israel, or any-- because the [?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Galut ?] was a part of God's will.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Everything that happened was God's will.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we had to stay in Poland at any time, even if the Germans will come in.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because God is not going to forsake his people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And as much as we til today don't believe or question the idea of having possibilities to come to America, or to any other country, there was a big possibility.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Because if you had a certain amount of money, you did not need even invitation to America.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You could go in, as a capitalist.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And my father had some money.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But the Rebbe said, God forbid.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You don't leave the country.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And so the influence is very-- and while he did not believe in it 100%, but he said, if the Rebbe said, in absolute terms, God forbid, you were not to break it.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And so we stayed in Poland [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] to rely on God through the Rebbe.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Number two, I was thinking lately, we had developed this idea-- you probably heard it-- [NON-ENGLISH], the 36 holy men.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
